Remarks: Second test of booster landing legs on drone ship.
First test of booster landing legs landing on a mobile ship platform.
SpaceX tested thier booster landing legs for the second time.
Third stage failure at T+542 seconds. Turbo-pump pipe leak.
Carried two student built satellites via the 3 Corner Satellite program. It failed to reach orbit however.
First Delta IV launch into a LEO/SSO
First Delta IV launch contracted by United Launch Alliance
Launch delayed due to damage to launch pad caused by a liquid oxygen leak
